<TEXT>
MAYTAG, the US household appliance group, yesterday said deteriorating
business in Europe offset improved North American sales and resulted in a
slightly lower operating net for its second quarter, Reuter reports.
The group reported a net profit of Dollars 23.3m, or 22 cents a share,
