before the charge. Sales edged down to Dollars 770m from Dollars 778m a year
ago.
The company's North American appliance group had sales of Dollars 567.4m,
against Dollars 566.8m a year ago. But operating income of Dollars 46.3m was
off 10 per cent because of start-up costs for a new dishwasher plant and
several new electric range models, and the cost of discontinuing operations
at its previous dishwasher facility.
