John Allison, until recently a marketing consultant, is joining The LIFE
ASSOCIATION OF SCOTLAND, a subsidiary of Internationale Nederlanden Group,
as general manager (marketing).
*****
John Fairbanks is taking up the newly created post of sales promotion
director at SUN LIFE OF CANADA; he returns to the company after spending the
