John Labatt        (Brewing)           Royal Trust  (Financial Services)
MacMillan Bloedel  (Forestry)          Trizec       (Real Estate)
Norcen             (Oil and gas)       Bramalea     (Real Estate)
Royal LePage       (Property services)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
